comments: Kuminga (GSW) reaches in for the ball and Doncic (DAL) raises his off-arm to draw attention to the marginal contact.
Green (DAL) is firming up behind Kuminga (GSW) when the defender steps back slightly and marginal contact occurs.
Green (DAL) reestablishes himself in a screening position on Kuminga's (GSW) side and briefly grasps and relinquishes the back of Kuminga's jersey as he moves around the defender.
Green (GSW) legally contests Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) perimeter shot attempt.
Wiggins (GSW) establishes himself in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and he firms up as the defender moves into the pick. The contact on the play is marginal.
Doncic (DAL) lowers his arm down and makes contact with the ball that dislodges it from Curry's (GSW) grasp during the driving shot attempt. The contact after the dislodge is considered incidental.
Doncic (DAL) dislodges the ball from Curry (GSW) and the loose ball deflects off of Curry's right knee and bounces out of bounds. Possession is properly awarded to Dallas.
Doncic (DAL) and Kuminga (GSW) come together away from the ball and the contact is marginal.
Wiggins (GSW) aligns along Green's (DAL) path and lowers his left arm down and some marginal contact occurs with Green's lower body during the driving shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Doncic's (DAL) path and marginal contact occurs during the screen.
Doncic (DAL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) driving shot attempt.
Finney-Smith (DAL) establishes himself in Poole's (GSW) path and Poole avoids contact as he goes over the top of the pick.
Poole (GSW) steps towards Green's (DAL) space after he gathers the ball and marginal body contact occurs.
Doncic (DAL) briefly brings his left arm around Wiggins' (GSW) left arm and slides it off with the entry pass imminent.
Wiggins (GSW) reaches in for the ball and Doncic (DAL) lifts his off-arm to draw attention to the marginal contact at the start of the drive.
Kleber (DAL) slides his left arm off of Curry's (GSW) arm during Doncic's (DAL) drive and the contact is marginal.

Doncic (DAL) and Curry (GSW) come together at the same spot on the floor and Doncic braces for the marginal contact with his off-arm. His off-arm comes out slightly as two player's move apart after the marginal contact.
Poole (GSW) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and Finney-Smith brings his left arm around Green's back and dislodges the offensive player while fighting over the pick.
During the inbound, Kleber (DAL) uses his shoulder to deliver contact to Poole (GSW) and affect his FOM.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path but continuously reestablishes into the defender, which inhibits his movement around the screen.
Green (DAL) reaches in for the ball and dislodges it as Wiggins (GSW) attempts to corral the pass. The arm contact after the initial dislodge is considered incidental.
Thompson (GSW) receives the pass and begins his upward shooting motion and fumbles the ball.  Due to the fumble, he is legally able to obtain the loose ball.
Wiggins (GSW) is moving along Doncic's (DAL) path when marginal contact occurs as Doncic brings the ball up the floor.
Green (DAL) establishes himself in Wiggins' (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs as the players come together during the pick.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in Thompson's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs as Hardawar Jr. releases away after setting the pick.
Poole (GSW) beats Hardaway (DAL) to the spot and absorbs the contact during his drive to the basket.
Wiggins (GSW) legally contests Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) firms up on his left foot and marginal contact occurs as Finney-Smith (DAL) moves into the pick.

Curry (GSW) gathers the ball on his right foot and steps back with his left foot coming down and then his right foot. This establishes his left foot as his pivot foot. Curry proceeds to lift and replant his left pivot foot during his pump fake.
Curry (GSW) commits a take foul on Green (DAL).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in Kuminga's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs as Kuminga fights over the screen.
Wiggins (GSW) commits a take foul on Finney-Smith (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) and Kuminga (GSW) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Looney (GSW) and Kleber (DAL) mutually engage during the rebound and marginal contact occurs.
Curry (GSW) absorbs the initial contact that occurs with Finney-Smith (DAL) and marginal contact occurs as Finney-Smith (DAL) attempts to move around the screen.
Poole (GSW) and Hardaway Jr. (DAL) mutually engage and disengage during the inbound and the contact is marginal.
Finney-Smith (DAL) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) perimeter shot attempt.
